Input : 6
Expected Output: 
     #
    ##
   ###
  ####
 #####
######

Solution in Java: // Below method accepts integer as parameter to print the staircase
    public static void staircase(int n) {
        for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++) {
            for (int j = i; j < n; j++) {
                System.out.print(" ");
            }
            for (int k = 0; k < i; k++) {
                System.out.print("#");
            }
            System.out.println();
        }
    }
